{"tid":394152,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"好掛住東橫inn...","createTime":"2017-09-09T17:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T04:17:04.000Z","uid":60219,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da5650d98ea8d05637a5e43e7a76bcca5a4688ff","tid":394152,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:02:09.000Z","msg":"我知實有人話我癡線，東橫inn咁老土<br />\n<br />\n但每次諗返起佢間房永遠如一嘅格局同擺設<br />\n<br />\n好撚暖嘅棉被<br />\n<br />\n洗手間花王洗頭水嘅氣味<br />\n<br />\n就覺得好懷念，之前去日本玩嘅回憶都湧曬出嚟...<br />\n<br />\n啊!!!!!我好掛住東橫inn啊!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://7.share.photo.xuite.net/pswo210525/1726b6a/19611350/1093015444_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F7.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fpswo210525%2F1726b6a%2F19611350%2F1093015444_l.jpg&h=e9c4815c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e71eec2dc0a0478c4bb91f884e9e5541f9644422","tid":394152,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"住過一次<br />\n真係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b8836778bf7c4a5de3e651b536a4e4bac2de9e","tid":394152,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:04:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c70c1aae88b1066e644b42972f76a042f4bdf762","tid":394152,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"個一人"},{"pid":"385fb8101716053e34cd819c6b659d3935160e0a","tid":394152,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住過一次<br />\n真係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開大冷氣攤係張140cm既床到，大大力索張床既氣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c0653133db6e56c89b5c1ec499fcf1dd28dd2f","tid":394152,"uid":60219,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:08:17.000Z","msg":"東橫inn既早餐...<br />\n<br />\n比我老母煮得更加有家既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7548/16024635370_053b477081_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7548%2F16024635370_053b477081_c.jpg&h=687c3bcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d136f53e9b77b83d3b08ad778d433789f8a1fd8f","tid":394152,"uid":60219,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"東橫inn既大堂好溫暖啊...<br />\n<br />\n點似得屋企樓下得個西口西面既保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.backpackerwebs.com/japan-kyushu/files/2015/07/DSCN3236.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.backpackerwebs.com%2Fjapan-kyushu%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F07%2FDSCN3236.jpg&h=8b6f963d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0b1834f660b91dd89dafbed4263418641f41371","tid":394152,"uid":60219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:13:19.000Z","msg":"小而精巧既洗手間...<br />\n<br />\n諗起係個浴缸浸泡泡浴，又諗起花王洗頭水同沐浴露個氣味<br />\n<br />\n好正啊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-ltppDP56wYk/VLLCu28L_4I/AAAAAAAACyE/FZPniMP7bz0/w467-h701-no/SAM_5359.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-ltppDP56wYk%2FVLLCu28L_4I%2FAAAAAAAACyE%2FFZPniMP7bz0%2Fw467-h701-no%2FSAM_5359.JPG&h=b5f32d70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae0fbc99655a412f8b1539a6edb968ed417249f4","tid":394152,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"apa好住D <br />\n感覺光D 新D<br />\n<br />\n東橫感覺舊舊地"},{"pid":"10865429fd24938aa50e359e0bfea66151373900","tid":394152,"uid":60219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"總係覺得其他酒店走廊有股邪氣/妖氣，又有好大陣清潔完既味道<br />\n<br />\n但唯獨東橫inn既走廊，特別令人安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1560/26075063341_5cda7ef176_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm2.staticflickr.com%2F1560%2F26075063341_5cda7ef176_b.jpg&h=c43d4676&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53dbdfc9c3f74974f206354b419e438086363d72","tid":394152,"uid":60219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:17:31.000Z","msg":"屋企鎖匙...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/0f/bb/02/50/905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-cdn.tripadvisor.com%2Fmedia%2Fphoto-s%2F0f%2Fbb%2F02%2F50%2F905.jpg&h=3a0c1836&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26bc17ee86db9b83a21576043d95fa88a948ea95","tid":394152,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都好掛住去日本住嘅果幾間酒店"},{"pid":"c3d58b313d12ef3660211f20461acb29db154780","tid":394152,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"張檯啊...盞燈啊...風筒啊...<br />\n<br />\n仲有獨立冷氣啊!!屌打曬其他用中央冷氣系統既酒店!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm8.static.flickr.com/7340/13004760864_2d94ae233e_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.static.flickr.com%2F7340%2F13004760864_2d94ae233e_o.jpg&h=1335aad4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2950bbf3dd4c0942f38c61bb579c13b715cf5a6","tid":394152,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都好掛住去日本住嘅果幾間酒店</blockquote><br />\nI know that feel啊!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cd225ed97e5ad